| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-3011 — Mass File Rename (ransomexx)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c41f6361-687c-542e-8269-156c31613db4"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
